text: Dalneye () is a rural locality (a selo) in Budarinsky Selsoviet, Limansky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 78 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 120 km from Astrakhan, 24 km from Liman. == References == Category:Rural localities in Limansky District
title: Dalneye, Astrakhan Oblast
